    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Tear the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong>&nbsp;into&nbsp;large bite-sized pieces&nbsp;(this saves time and creates an interesting texture)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1428.-step-1-x200.jpg",
