            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the&nbsp;<strong>torn chestnut mushrooms</strong> to a baking tray with the&nbsp;<strong>butternut squash cubes&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 25 min, or until the <strong>vegetables</strong> are golden and softened</p>",
